        "content": "## Workflow 3: Nashville Lead Generation Email Drip\n\n**Trigger:** Google Sheets — new row added to \"Nashville Leads\" sheet with status = \"new\"\n\n**Sheet columns:**\nlead_name, lead_email, lead_phone, lead_type (residential/commercial), source, date_added, status, contacted_date, response_date, follow_up_2_date, final_date, outcome\n\n**Sequence:**\n- Day 0: Intro email → mark \"contacted\"\n- Day 3: Social proof email (if not responded)\n- Day 7: Final educational email (if not responded) → mark \"sequence_complete\"\n\n**NOTE:** To pause sequence when lead responds, update the sheet row status to \"responded\" — the IF nodes will stop further emails.",
        "height": 340,
        "width": 420
