    {
      "parameters": {
        "sendTo": "={{ $json.lead_email }}",
        "subject": "Indoor air quality testing in Nashville — are you protected?",
        "emailType": "html",
        "message": "<p>Hi {{ $json.lead_name }},</p>\n\n<p>My name is Martine Davis, and I'm the owner of <strong>Indoor Environmental Testing Inc.</strong> — a specialized environmental inspection company serving the Nashville area (and Madison, WI) for the past several years.</p>\n\n<p>{{ $json.greeting }}, you already know that what's <em>inside</em> your property matters just as much as what's outside. But most people don't realize that indoor air can be 2–5x more polluted than outdoor air — even in brand-new construction.</p>\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #2E7D32;\">What we test for:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Mold &amp; Mycotoxins</strong> — especially critical in Nashville's humid climate</li>\n  <li><strong>Air Quality (VOCs, particulates, CO2)</strong> — from building materials, furniture, and HVAC systems</li>\n  <li><strong>EMF &amp; RF Radiation</strong> — from smart meters, cell towers, and wireless devices</li>\n  <li><strong>Chemical Contaminants</strong> — radon, pesticides, and off-gassing materials</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>We use certified, laboratory-grade equipment and provide detailed reports with actionable recommendations — not just a list of numbers you can't interpret.</p>\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #2E7D32;\">Why Nashville clients choose IET:</h3>\n<p>Nashville's rapid growth means a lot of new construction, renovation, and older homes being repurposed. We've seen firsthand how water intrusion during building, humidity fluctuations, and new materials off-gassing can silently impact the health of families and employees.</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;\">\n  <a href=\"YOUR_APPTOTAL_BOOKING_LINK\" style=\"background-color: #2E7D32; color: white; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 16px;\">Schedule a Free Consultation</a>\n</p>\n\n<p>If you have questions or want to talk through what type of testing might be right for your {{ $json.lead_type_label }}, feel free to reply to this email or call us directly.</p>\n\n<p>We look forward to helping you create a healthier indoor environment.</p>\n\n<p>Warmly,<br>\n<strong>Martine Davis</strong><br>\nIndoor Environmental Testing Inc.<br>\nNashville, TN | Madison, WI<br>\nPhone: YOUR_PHONE_NUMBER<br>\n<a href=\"mailto:martine@indoorenvironmentaltesting.com\">martine@indoorenvironmentaltesting.com</a><br>\n<a href=\"YOUR_WEBSITE_URL\">www.indoorenvironmentaltesting.com</a></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #999; font-size: 11px;\">You're receiving this because you expressed interest in indoor environmental testing services. To unsubscribe, reply with \"unsubscribe\" in the subject line.</p>",
        "options": {
          "replyTo": "martine@indoorenvironmentaltesting.com"
        }
      },
