    {
      "parameters": {
        "sendTo": "={{ $json.lead_email }}",
        "subject": "One last thing about your home's air quality",
        "emailType": "html",
        "message": "<p>Hi {{ $json.lead_name }},</p>\n\n<p>I'll keep this brief — I know your inbox is busy.</p>\n\n<p>I wanted to share one fact that surprises almost every Nashville client we work with:</p>\n\n<blockquote style=\"border-left: 4px solid #2E7D32; padding: 12px 20px; margin: 20px 0; background: #f9f9f9; font-size: 16px;\">\n  <strong>Mold is the #1 hidden indoor air quality risk in Nashville homes</strong> — and it's almost entirely due to humidity.\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>Nashville's average indoor relative humidity regularly exceeds 60% during summer months. Mold begins growing at 55–60% humidity and can become a serious health concern within days of a water intrusion event — even a small one.</p>\n\n<p>The challenge is that mold often grows inside walls, under flooring, or in HVAC ducts where you can't see it. By the time you smell it, it's usually widespread.</p>\n\n<p><strong>A professional mold inspection takes about 2 hours</strong> and gives you a complete picture of your indoor environment — including air sampling and surface testing if needed.</p>\n\n<p>If you're not ready to book yet, I'm happy to answer any questions you have via email — no pressure, no sales pitch. Just straightforward information about what testing can and can't tell you.</p>\n\n<p>Reply to this email anytime, or use the link below if you'd like to schedule.</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;\">\n  <a href=\"YOUR_APPTOTAL_BOOKING_LINK\" style=\"background-color: #2E7D32; color: white; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 16px;\">Schedule an Inspection</a>\n</p>\n\n<p>Thank you for your time, {{ $json.lead_name }}. Whether we work together now or down the road, I hope this information has been helpful.</p>\n\n<p>Take care,<br>\n<strong>Martine Davis</strong><br>\nIndoor Environmental Testing Inc.<br>\nNashville, TN | Madison, WI<br>\nPhone: YOUR_PHONE_NUMBER</p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #999; font-size: 11px;\">This is the final email in our Nashville outreach sequence. You won't hear from us again unless you reach out. To unsubscribe permanently, reply with \"unsubscribe.\"</p>",
        "options": {
          "replyTo": "martine@indoorenvironmentaltesting.com"
        }
      },
